description:
This is a 16 minute workout called '15-minute POST-WORKOUT STRETCH for Injury Prevention & Flexibility' from the channel Kaleigh Cohen Strength.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Comfort Moves vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Let's RELAX! After a tough workout, you deserve a refreshing post-workout stretch. Join me for 15 minutes as we work through several full-body stretches to increase your flexibility and decompress. Our stretch session will help to relieve tight muscles in your back, hips, upper body, and legs, and WOW it feels awesome to release those tight muscles! Stretching is a great way to prevent injuries and relieve low back aches so be sure to add this stretch often to your training regimen.
